{"article_id":"s9FlOqC1pHyAdr5l","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Ousted Defense Secretary Chuck Hagel had become `` very , very frustrated '' in the post","depth":8},{"id":1,"text":"before President Obama sought his resignation ,","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"according to a key lawmaker ,","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"who blasted the White House for a whispering campaign","depth":9},{"id":4,"text":"that accompanied the Pentagon boss ' abrupt ouster Monday morning .","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"\" I thank Chuck Hagel for his service ,","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"and I know","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"that he was very , very frustrated , \"","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"Sen. John McCain , the Arizona Republican","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"who is expected to take control of the Senate Armed Services Committee in January ,","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"said in a radio interview with KFYI .","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"McCain spoke","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"following a Rose Garden press conference","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"at which Hagel stood stiffly","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"while Obama announced","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"he would be stepping down .","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"Although McCain ,","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"who served in the Senate with Hagel from 1996-2008 ,","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"opposed his fellow Vietnam veteran 's appointment to defense secretary ,","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"he said","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"administration sources were wrong","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"to assail Hagel on his way out the door .","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"\" Already White House people are leaking ,","depth":11},{"id":23,"text":"' Well , he wasn ' t up to the job , ' ''","depth":11},{"id":24,"text":"McCain said .","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"`` Well , believe me ,","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"he was up to the job .","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"It was the job","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"he was given ,","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"where he really was never really brought into that real tight circle inside the White House","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"that makes all the decisions","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"which has put us into the incredible debacle","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"that we ' re in today throughout the world . \"","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"McCain noted","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"that Hagel characterized the Islamic State as the greatest threat in the Middle East ,","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"while Obama was calling them the jayvee","depth":11},{"id":36,"text":"( junior varsity )","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"team less than a year ago .","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"He also criticized Obama","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"for failing in areas like the Middle East , Ukraine , and responding to a newly aggressive China .","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"\" We ' ve had our disagreements","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"but Chuck Hagel is an honorable man , \"","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"McCain added .","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"At the news conference , Obama said","depth":5},{"id":44,"text":"Hagel concluded","depth":6},{"id":45,"text":"it ' s an \" appropriate time \"","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"for him","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"to complete his service .","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"Hagel has had a rocky tenure of nearly two years","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"in which he 's struggled to break through the White House 's insular foreign policy team .","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"He stepped down under pressure amid multiple foreign policy crises ,","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"including the rise of the Islamic State group .","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"But in remarks at the White House , Obama praised Hagel as `` an exemplary defense secretary '' and steady hand for strategy and budget .","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"Obama said","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"he 'll always be grateful","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"that Hagel has always `` given it to me straight . ''","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"The Vietnam veteran and former Republican senator took office less than two years ago ,","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"and was charged with overseeing the winding down of decade-long wars in Afghanistan and Iraq .","depth":7},{"id":58,"text":"Hagel , 68 , also steered the military during sweeping changes","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"involving gays and women in the military .","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"But in recent months , the Pentagon has taken on new challenges ,","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"including fighting Islamic State in Syria and Iraq","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"and deploying military personnel to Africa","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"to fight Ebola .","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"Sources told FoxNews.com","depth":6},{"id":65,"text":"that Obama 's dissatisfaction with Hagel , as well as a desire","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"to shake up the cabinet","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"following the devastating midterm elections ,","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"played a role","depth":7},{"id":69,"text":"in the president seeking Hagel 's ouster .","depth":5},{"id":70,"text":"\" Make no mistake ,","depth":7},{"id":71,"text":"Secretary Hagel was fired , \"","depth":7},{"id":72,"text":"a senior U.S. official with close knowledge of the situation told Fox News .","depth":6},{"id":73,"text":"This same official discounted Pentagon claims","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"it was a mutual decision","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"claiming","depth":8},{"id":76,"text":"President Obama has lost confidence in Hagel","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"and that the White House had been planning to announce his exit for weeks .","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"\" The president felt","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"he had to fire someone .","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"He fired the only Republican in his cabinet .","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"Who is that going to piss off","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"that he cares about ? ''","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"In a swipe at the resume of Hagel ,","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"who served as U.S. Army sergeant in Vietnam","depth":11},{"id":85,"text":"and received two Purple Hearts ,","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"the official added ,","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"\" This is why you don ' t send a sergeant","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"to do a secretary ' s job . \"","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"Hagel took office Feb. 27 , 2013 ,","depth":5},{"id":90,"text":"five years after retiring from the Senate .","depth":5},{"id":91,"text":"Prior to his political career , Hagel co-founded Vanguard Cellular ,","depth":6},{"id":92,"text":"worked for an investment banking firm","depth":7},{"id":93,"text":"and ran American Information Systems , a company","depth":8},{"id":94,"text":"that makes computerized voting machines .","depth":8},{"id":95,"text":"He also taught at Georgetown University","depth":6},{"id":96,"text":"after stepping down from the Senate .","depth":6},{"id":97,"text":"A senior defense official said","depth":6},{"id":98,"text":"that Hagel submitted his resignation letter to Obama Monday morning","depth":7},{"id":99,"text":"and that the president accepted it .","depth":7},{"id":100,"text":"Hagel agreed to remain in office","depth":7},{"id":101,"text":"until his successor is confirmed by the Senate ,","depth":7},{"id":102,"text":"the official said .","depth":6},{"id":103,"text":"The president is not expected to nominate a new Pentagon chief Monday ,","depth":6},{"id":104,"text":"according to one official .","depth":6},{"id":105,"text":"The officials insisted on anonymity","depth":6},{"id":106,"text":"because they were not authorized to discuss the matter by name ahead of Obama 's official announcement .","depth":6},{"id":107,"text":"Hagel , the only Republican on Obama ' s cabinet , served as senator from Nebraska for two terms ,","depth":6},{"id":108,"text":"beginning in 1996 ,","depth":6},{"id":109,"text":"and became a critic of U.S. involvement in Iraq .","depth":5},{"id":110,"text":"Obama nominated him","depth":5},{"id":111,"text":"to succeed Leon Panetta as Defense Secretary in his second term .","depth":5},{"id":112,"text":"Recent questions about Hagel 's future at the Pentagon were prompted in part by his decision","depth":5},{"id":113,"text":"to postpone a long-planned trip this month to Vietnam .","depth":5},{"id":114,"text":"At the time , officials said","depth":6},{"id":115,"text":"he needed to remain in Washington for congressional consultations ,","depth":6},{"id":116,"text":"but that did not stop speculation","depth":6},{"id":117,"text":"that the White House might be looking for a replacement for the final two years of Obama 's term .","depth":6},{"id":118,"text":"Just last week , Hagel was asked about the speculation during an interview on the Charlie Rose show .","depth":7},{"id":119,"text":"He was asked","depth":8},{"id":120,"text":"whether he 's concerned by the speculation .","depth":8},{"id":121,"text":"`` No .","depth":7},{"id":122,"text":"First of all , I serve at the pleasure of the president , ''","depth":8},{"id":123,"text":"Hagel said .","depth":8},{"id":124,"text":"`` I 'm immensely grateful for the opportunity","depth":8},{"id":125,"text":"I 've had the last two years","depth":8},{"id":126,"text":"to work every day for the country and for the men and women","depth":8},{"id":127,"text":"who serve this country .","depth":8},{"id":128,"text":"I do n't get up in the morning","depth":7},{"id":129,"text":"and worry about my job .","depth":7},{"id":130,"text":"It ` s not unusual by the way , to change teams at different times . ''","depth":4}],"relations":[{"parent":261,"left":227,"right":260,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":227,"left":194,"right":226,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":194,"left":173,"right":193,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":173,"left":146,"right":172,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":146,"left":141,"right":145,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":141,"left":135,"right":140